# CSS Layers

| File | npm export | Contains |
|---|---|---|
| `src/shutters-core.css` | `core.css` | Grid animation, motion, focus ring, clean dividers |
| `src/shutters-theme.css` | `theme.css` | Optional colors, hover, content typography |
| `demo/shutters-demo.css` | — | Demo page layout only |

Core is theme-less but visually polished. Never put decorative colors in core.

## Motion (do not revert to max-height)

- `grid-template-rows: 0fr → 1fr` with `transition-behavior: allow-discrete`
- Opacity on `.shutters-body`, not `.shutters-content`
- `--shutters-animation-easing` (open) vs `--shutters-animation-easing-close`

## After CSS changes

- [ ] `npm run sync:demo`
- [ ] `npm run build` && `npm test`
- [ ] `npm run agent:sync`
